Flex direction

Dealing with spacing:

Parent: ie View

alignItems
justifyContent
flexDirection

Child: ie Text

flex
alignSelf


------------ Position Property -------------

position by default is 'relative'


----------   Overview ------------------

Apply box object model rules > is postion 'absolute' > 
YES > Apply some flex box rules, ignore all sibblings
NO > Aplly all flex box rules, considering siblings > Place element inside parent > appl top, left, bottom, right
